{"tid":1925589,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者：卸責徒添國際反感","createTime":"2020-03-14T13:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T14:45:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b28ebf8110e962fb202bf5528dc721b1f5099e2c","tid":1925589,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/6RXMLWDBKYFES75USUHKZH5S7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2F6RXMLWDBKYFES75USUHKZH5S7A%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCfcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=c3dcc452\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2F6RXMLWDBKYFES75USUHKZH5S7A%2F&h=76955f97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/6RXMLWDBKYFES75USUHKZH5S7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n學者：卸責徒添國際反感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200314/large/1584116721_0c64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200314%2Flarge%2F1584116721_0c64.jpg&h=4e89dfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共黨史學者章立凡（圖）認為，趙立堅在Twitter指控疑為美軍帶病毒到武漢絕非他個人之舉，也並非偶然，而是中共企圖洗脫「病毒輸出國」形象，推卸給其他國家。不過，他認為中共的如意算盤不會打得響，因為現在國內對中共的輿情也已一觸即發，趙立堅的言論只會徒添國際間的反感。<br />\n<br />\n章立凡指，趙立堅突在Twitter連環發文，肯定是中國「大甩鍋（推卸責任）」的其中一步。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習憂「罪己就會亡國」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：倫敦返港 16月大男嬰染疫<br />\n<br />\n章立凡指，退一步來說，就算中國真的不是新型冠狀病毒的源頭，中國政府在爆發初期隱瞞疫情，導致全球大流行，這個責任是無論如何都「甩不開」的。他又指，中共的體制不是人民授權，本就沒有認受性，是不容許道歉，加上中共總書記習近平擔心亡黨，更不會認錯，「毛澤東說過，罪己就會亡國，他的隔代徒弟也是這個思路」，所以中國也企圖扭轉病毒輸出國的國際形象，指控素有恩怨的美國，但是騙不了國內民眾，也騙不了國際。"},{"pid":"fd03a06674410d57f729fda47e99529b6bc6ccc8","tid":1925589,"uid":23085,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"好心<br />\n連牆內中國人都唔信<br />\n佢個twitter撐佢嘅好多都係無follower嘅網軍小粉紅<br />\n我地要落力d唔好俾中共咁易spin風向"},{"pid":"a06021d32b31c0d43a49c1009e41290a90025127","tid":1925589,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea09c0c8676b4e5bcf0efeb4d48f4d096caea84","tid":1925589,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"喺牆內打飛機都唔夠, 係要走去人地twitter, 等於喺屋企打唔夠要去人屋企打到一地都係仲要問人怕未"},{"pid":"a8bc4abac195df2ff942701f1f03676ff1676da4","tid":1925589,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"本來諗住佢會講下外國點樣唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知輕輕帶過咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf03ac51f609e7766445476662030b2c9f945e3","tid":1925589,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bc4abac195df2ff942701f1f03676ff1676da4","tid":1925589,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"本來諗住佢會講下外國點樣唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知輕輕帶過咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"佢淨係講呢一番說話都隨時已經冇命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a06debeeffe1801128889eb9d101daa010d349b","tid":1925589,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"但意粉信到十足十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15002007d6f07f73ac7f82a3c5dcb9f2f426ece8","tid":1925589,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"真心係騙到鄰蝈人，都呃到唔少藍屍<br />\n因為佢地踏出咗信仰之躍 唔願意相信對自己不利嘅野<br />\n共產党死 佢地都甘願做炮灰"},{"pid":"e53eb8b147ab2daf104a59aa9a8336b8a6ec3885","tid":1925589,"uid":62194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:45:03.000Z",